{
  "info": {
    "name": "RFQ Marketplace API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the RFQ (Request for Quotation) Marketplace platform. This API enables users to create RFQs and companies to submit quotations.\n\n**Framework:** Yii2 PHP Framework\n**Authentication:** JWT Bearer Token\n**Base URL:** {{base_url}}/v1\n\n**Roles:**\n- **User:** Can create RFQs, view quotations, accept/reject quotations\n- **Company:** Can browse RFQs, submit quotations, manage subscriptions\n\n**Getting Started:**\n1. Register an account (user or company)\n2. Login to receive JWT token\n3. Set the `jwt_token` variable with your token\n4. Start making authenticated requests",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{jwt_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "jwt_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
